name: ZooKeeper
0:
”Alexa, ask Zoo Keeper, what does a zebra say?”
”Alexa, tell Zoo Keeper to make a sound like a whale.”
”Alexa, ask Zoo Keeper, what's new?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: zoo keeper
des:
Ask Zoo Keeper to play the sound of an animal. If she knows it, she will. Find out once and for all: what does the fox say?

Update 2018-01-15: Zoo Keeper learned the sound of sheep, bears and even giraffes.
